edited <filename>/etc/irda/drivers</filename> to include <command>irattach /dev/ttyS0</command> (or whatever your "serial" IrDA port is, WH). Also <filename>/etc/conf.modules</filename> contains <command>alias tty-ldisc-11 irtty</command>.
