<TITLE>Configuration</TITLE>

<PARA>
By Florian Lohoff &lt;flo@rfc822.org&gt;: "Do it step by step - Get your irda working <command>irmanager -d 1</command>, <command>irattach /dev/ttySx</command> etc. Then have a look at the <filename>/proc/net/irda/discovery</filename> whether you find something like this:
</PARA>

